hcc_text: Macombs Dam Branch is a pedestrian high crash corridor (top 10% for pedestrian deaths and serious injuries per mile in the Bronx)
info: At Macombs Dam Branch at Major Deegan Exwy Sb Exit 5 and Deegan Exwy Sb En Macombs Dam Branch, there was one injury in crashes between 2008 and 2012.
